data.meta_description: The most popular baby names, including the 1000 most popular names in the U.S. and on Nameberry and the 100 most popular names in other countries around the world.
data.text:
What are the most popular names on Nameberry, in the US, and around the world? This page is your jumping off point to search names by popularity using every baby name popularity list we could find. We tally our own list of popular girl names and popular boy names each month, so you know what the trending baby names are in real time. And we carry official lists the Top 1000 Baby Names for 2023 in the US, the full Top 1000 popular names by state, the roster of top names in the UK, and many others. Read on to learn which baby names are trending where.

Top Baby Names Brazil

The top baby names in Brazil in 2023 feature Helena as the Number 1 girl name, and Miguel leading the way for boys. Alice, Laura, Gael and Theo are also among the most popular Brazilian names, as are double names like João Miguel and Maria Clara. Brazil’s baby name charts are published by the Civil Registry.
